Package: FinReturns
Title: Financial Asset Return Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Rafael", "Conde Gomes", , "rafael@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements an S3 object system to analyze and visualize financial
    asset returns. It includes methods for calculating statistical moments
    (skewness, kurtosis) and generating defensive visualizations (time series,
    histograms, Q-Q plots) using 'ggplot2'. Includes S&P 500 data for demonstration.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports:
    ggplot2
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5)
